Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.16,0:00:15.27,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.27,0:00:16.16,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:20.77,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.07,0:00:23.65,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Aquileia's bazaar is really popular,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:25.51,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,so the good stuff gets snapped up fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.51,0:00:27.37,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't move faster, \NI'll just go on without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:29.84,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come crying to me if you get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:36.11,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As a Void Mage, I am \Nresponsible for this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.19,0:00:41.46,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Louise... She has to contend \Nwith so much pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.45,0:00:45.00,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...with that little body of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.60,0:00:48.99,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:55.57,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to buy it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.02,0:00:58.90,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I do get my pay as a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.90,0:01:00.37,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I can afford it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.53,0:01:04.31,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I could get you a real mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.74,0:01:07.08,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,A real mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.83,0:01:12.12,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Living in a mansion, alone with Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:17.89,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:21.72,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's not always honest, she gets jealous,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.72,0:01:23.32,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and can be rather annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.25,0:01:27.85,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'm going to protect her,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.04,0:01:31.28,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:06.96,Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(625,1)}Aquileia's Shrine Maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:12.29,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.84,0:03:15.80,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, during the \Nthird anniversary celebration
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:19.07,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,of His Holiness' \Nascent here in Aquileia,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:20.95,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,it will be our duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:24.15,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,as the Order of the Undine Knights, \Nto ensure the safety of the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:27.93,CRZero,Reynald,0000,0000,0000,,Without further details, \Nthat sounds somewhat important.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:31.12,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality it's nothing \Nmore than crowd control.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:33.66,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Forward, Undine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:36.19,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,This city is so romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:39.88,CRZero,Kirch,0000,0000,0000,,It's like being on a honeymoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.94,0:03:45.45,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty rude of Miss \NVallière to cut out on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:46.20,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:49.95,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Louise and Tiffania have both...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:53.94,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,...accepted the role of shrine maiden \Nat His Holiness' celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:04:00.79,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Your Grace, please ensure their safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:02.56,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:05.48,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,Something like yesterday \Nwill not happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.49,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,Is that not so, Julio?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:08.49,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:11.25,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,For the entire two weeks of ceremonies,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:13.53,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,we have 300 holy knights \Nsecuring this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:15.17,CRZero,Agnès,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, just yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.91,0:04:18.50,CRZero,Agnès,0000,0000,0000,,the Founder's Round Mirror was stolen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:21.03,CRZero,Agnès,0000,0000,0000,,by mercenaries who call themselves \Nthe "Elemental Siblings."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:23.88,CRZero,Agnès,0000,0000,0000,,What about the possibility that those
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:26.54,CRZero,Agnès,0000,0000,0000,,who hired them are plotting a conspiracy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:28.66,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,We can't rule it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:35.55,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,However, we have prepared magic \Ndetection spells throughout the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:39.60,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who tries to use magic \Nwill be detected immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:41.09,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need for concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:46.29,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Agnès?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.93,CRZero,Agnès,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:51.25,CRZero,Agnès,0000,0000,0000,,I believe we are being too careless towards
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:52.57,CRZero,Agnès,0000,0000,0000,,an enemy we can't read.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:55.96,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,What concerns me the most \Nis that I could sense
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:58.88,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,that His Grace was not \Nshaken by yesterday's event.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.81,0:05:01.61,CRZero,Agnès,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying he expected it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:06.33,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I'm just making too much of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:18.06,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't it possible that it was
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:20.46,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saito who was summoned back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:34.78,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's happened again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:37.77,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just looking at him was enough \Nto make my heart race.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:40.22,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:47.58,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:51.06,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.00,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:58.27,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,L-Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:02.29,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,This is my shrine maiden \Noutfit for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:04.98,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to show it to you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:08.14,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,A holy maiden...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.25,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the presence of a holy maiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:14.17,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:15.82,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:19.92,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,L-Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:22.64,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,S-Saito, you mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:25.53,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that in the clothes \NI'm going to wear before God!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:29.40,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. You look so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:32.06,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:33.00,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:35.56,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You're like a... like a...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:37.34,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,...little lemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,0:06:40.43,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,A lemon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:42.15,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Your skin is smooth,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:43.56,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,your scent is soft...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:46.11,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You're a little lemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:47.27,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.27,0:06:51.06,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like you when you \Nget like this, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:53.15,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, you're a lemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:54.85,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help myself against \Nthis little lemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:59.58,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what you're talking \Nabout, but am I really a lemon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:00.88,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:04.65,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Try saying, "I'm a shy lemon."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:09.54,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm a shy lemon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:11.99,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What a cute lemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:13.26,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,She really is so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.85,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:18.79,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,This little lemon is happy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:25.05,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message from the wind sprite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.36,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Malicorne?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:29.74,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,The walls of this abode \Nare unexpectedly thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:32.52,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,Please consider your neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:33.90,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:36.87,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,And seriously, little lemon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:39.85,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I... I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:41.47,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:45.05,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,He made me say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:53.72,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:55.97,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,Flame under my contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:59.39,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,Flow to the place that I indicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:18.91,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,That makes it three.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:22.61,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Lord Bidalsha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:27.96,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The Fire Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:29.85,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,You used the power of the sprites
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:32.55,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,to seal the power of fire \Ninto this crystal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.23,0:08:34.83,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,To put it simply, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:38.00,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,But it is actually much more \Ncomplex and profound than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:41.48,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Then I have a question \Nfor you, Lord Bidalsha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:45.40,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,How much land can a stone \Nthis size conflagrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:46.60,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:50.98,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking about its potential \Nas a weapon of mass destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:53.34,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,A weapon of destruction?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:56.28,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,I was not told it would be used for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:09:00.80,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I'm merely proposing that we \Ndiscover new uses for this stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:03.06,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come and observe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:04.28,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,I must decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:06.44,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,I do not wish to take part in crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:11.42,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,You have the nerve to say \Nthat after you locked your
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:13.81,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,innocent daughter away on my orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.81,0:09:16.23,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,and used secret elven magic \Non Jörmungandr's armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:18.67,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,You've already done more than take part!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:22.17,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,But do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:24.43,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,And what about my muse, Sheffield?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:26.63,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,How are your preparations?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:30.21,CRZero,Shef,0000,0000,0000,,King Joseph, by tomorrow \Neverything will be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:33.59,CRZero,Shef,0000,0000,0000,,The Founder's Round Mirror and \Nthe other key ingredient...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:57.94,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,Honored Founder Brimir...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:10:00.55,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,May you protect the peace of Halkeginia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:04.25,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,May you keep this land pure for all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:07.75,CRZero,Maidens,0000,0000,0000,,May you protect the peace of Halkeginia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.28,0:10:12.00,CRZero,Maidens,0000,0000,0000,,May you keep this land pure for all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:15.64,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:19.65,CRZero,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to have one \Nmoment with His Holiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:22.42,CRZero,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,If I did that, I could die in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:24.24,CRZero,Reynald,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but it's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:27.31,CRZero,Reynald,0000,0000,0000,,Commoners can only get a glimpse \Nof him through the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:31.12,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,If you will be watching, \Nplease move to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:32.42,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't go this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:34.41,CRZero,Reynald,0000,0000,0000,,Malicorne!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:40.32,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,I hate this job!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:41.92,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, look at all those people!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:44.82,CRZero,Kirch,0000,0000,0000,,The knights must have their hands full.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:46.15,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.45,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,This way, Mademoiselle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.45,0:10:51.20,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Please, watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:53.63,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:02.66,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Today's ceremony is finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:04.40,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there are a lot \Nof fervent believers,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:05.58,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,even amongst the commoners!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:08.01,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Your standing does not matter \Nwhen it comes to faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:12.19,CRZero,Maid1,0000,0000,0000,,But commoners only pray to \NGod when they need something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:13.72,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:14.31,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:15.45,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:16.85,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:18.40,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:20.00,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait for me in the common room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.71,0:11:25.30,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Isn't that proof, though, that their \Nneed for God is even greater?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:25.30,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,My goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:33.55,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Nice job today, Tiffa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:37.08,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Saito! You, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:39.21,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was stand there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:43.10,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this will \Ngo on for two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:53.25,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:56.26,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to know if Saito \Nis my familiar or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:59.27,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do I have something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:04.49,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, may I ask you for a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:08.17,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, you know I'd do anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:12.65,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'd like you to kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:14.88,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's what this is about...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:16.11,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:17.52,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:19.38,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tiffa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:26.15,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If he really is my familiar, \Nonce we kiss, a rune should appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:28.89,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tiffa, we can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:31.06,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Which is not to say it \Ndoesn't make me happy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:33.05,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,that you want to kiss me, but you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:34.78,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,it's all so complicated...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:36.12,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:39.51,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't, I'll keep burning here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:42.71,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:44.61,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tiffa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.31,0:12:48.72,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure we can just take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:49.63,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:52.25,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,Let Guiche do some real work for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:59.26,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,S-Saito and Tiffa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:02.23,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, this isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:06.52,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:06.52,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:12.33,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,So, first you got a lemon, \Nand then you want a melon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:15.01,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:17.61,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, why are all guys idiots?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:20.32,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:22.09,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:24.28,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:27.29,CRZero,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:32.81,CRZero,Maid1,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but commoners \Nare not allowed in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:36.54,CRZero,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're Miss Louise of House \NVallière, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:38.10,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:44.42,CRZero,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I work as a farmer on the land \Nthat Lord Vallière controls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:45.84,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You're part of our fiefdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:47.02,CRZero,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:50.68,CRZero,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Please, won't you have mercy on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:56.38,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:14:00.66,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You came with your mother \Nto see the ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:02.24,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:05.57,CRZero,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, my mother collapsed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:08.36,CRZero,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,when we entered the city, \Nmaybe from exhaustion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:12.34,CRZero,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure if you visited her \Nas a holy shrine maiden,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:14.53,CRZero,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,she would feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:17.14,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise left the holy halls?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:18.33,CRZero,Maid1,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:20.22,CRZero,Maid1,0000,0000,0000,,This common girl asked her for a favor
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:21.87,CRZero,Maid1,0000,0000,0000,,and I guess she couldn't refuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:23.93,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:25.23,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:28.98,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she always have \Nto do these random things?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:32.98,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:34.15,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:35.59,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:39.97,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:44.16,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:53.20,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you do that to Jacques?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:56.67,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:02.61,CRZero,Knights,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:04.19,CRZero,Knights,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:11.39,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,Easy as pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.94,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is he doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:16.06,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hope he hasn't done \Nanything with Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:22.53,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done repaying you \Nfor my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:24.77,CRZero,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,She's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:27.29,CRZero,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:29.11,CRZero,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Louise has come to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:34.35,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You've traveled a long way from \NVallière's lands to get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:35.75,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:42.59,CRZero,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I do hate these common clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:43.90,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:45.50,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:47.27,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Jeanette.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:50.64,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,That was my older brother you \Ndefeated a few days back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.29,0:15:56.29,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:01.11,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,This knife is poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.38,0:16:02.79,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:06.57,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,It paralyzes the body only temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:08.93,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:15.95,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:19.31,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,You've got quite the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:22.57,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's why they want you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:25.76,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,Stop getting involved, \Nyou child of the elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:28.29,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take over from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:29.82,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,You can go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:31.30,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:33.87,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I leave now, \Nyou'll have to pay in full.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:36.50,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,Your employer is telling you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:39.74,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then I leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:44.23,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,We might have become good friends
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:47.82,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,had we met under different circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:49.89,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:59.99,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go and pay a \Nvisit to our great master?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:14.00,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,Doudou?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:18.38,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:21.31,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,And it was just getting interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:28.11,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What did you guys do to Louise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.16,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.46,0:17:32.82,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,She's really cute and nice and innocent...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:35.18,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, I'd say she's a little too nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:36.81,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Louise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:38.78,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,A really scary lady took her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:40.81,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,They've probably left the city by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:43.35,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,Jeanette, stop talking so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:46.21,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,Damian will blame me for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:47.89,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:50.25,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,Our work is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:55.35,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:01.44,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:03.53,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:06.46,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All because I was so careless...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:13.71,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise... Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:16.91,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:31.89,CRZero,Agnès,0000,0000,0000,,I found this in an alley not \Nfar from the holy halls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.62,0:18:34.76,CRZero,Agnès,0000,0000,0000,,I am certain it belongs to Miss Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:37.29,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:40.28,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,My deepest apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:44.07,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,That such a vile act would \Noccur in broad daylight...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:46.54,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,And without using magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:49.84,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,This is Gallia's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:51.52,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.79,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,I called her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:57.44,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,She has a history with \Nthe Elemental Siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:58.98,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Please help us, Tabitha.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:01.92,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,They belong to the Knights of the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:05.86,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,North Parterre of Gallia, as I once did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:09.33,CRZero,Agnès,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that there is a special order
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:11.92,CRZero,Agnès,0000,0000,0000,,of knights in Gallia just for dirty work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:14.56,CRZero,Agnès,0000,0000,0000,,That means the true mastermind is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:17.50,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,The king of Gallia, Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:21.56,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,So Joseph has kidnapped Louise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:25.18,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,But if that is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:28.81,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Gallia's borders are very close to ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.86,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Louise might have crossed the border...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:33.92,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,My liege!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.26,0:19:37.46,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if I have to enter Gallia, \NI'm going to rescue Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:39.90,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:41.74,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, you'll also get...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.69,0:19:44.53,CRZero,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,My deepest apologies for this disturbance,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:47.48,CRZero,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,but there is something I must \Ndivulge to His Holiness at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:49.33,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,Come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:03.25,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,I think it would be best if \Neveryone here hears this as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:06.58,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,There has been a message sent by our \Ntroops patrolling the Gallian border.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.44,0:20:11.09,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,The Gallian fleet is \Nencroaching on our borders...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:13.14,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:15.48,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,But Your Holiness... Then, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.29,0:20:19.83,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,It means they may invade our lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:40.25,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,Is the young miss finally awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:44.94,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:46.00,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,Come, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:49.82,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I take orders \Nfrom just anybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:52.95,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning to do with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:54.98,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,If it's something horrible, \NI'll just bite my tongue off
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:57.47,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,and make myself bleed to \Ndeath before you get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:20:59.23,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Calm yourself, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:00.77,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:04.17,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I am Joseph, the king of Gallia,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:07.25,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,but I know they call me \N"The Incompetent King" in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.73,0:21:11.08,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:15.80,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I am not going to mistreat a school \Nfriend of my niece Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:19.98,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Like I can believe you after \Nwhat you did to Tabitha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:24.82,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Locking up a niece still reeks \Nof something a human would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:29.57,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm going to do next \Nis something that only demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.57,0:21:30.84,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,without a shred of humanity, would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.51,0:21:38.01,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,But to do that, you'll have \Nto lend me your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.47,0:21:41.30,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you wish to or not, \Nyou will witness it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:45.71,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The hell that will be born \Nonce the elven spells
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:47.99,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,and Void magic are combined.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:53.00,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saito... Saito.... Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.36,0:23:30.77,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,King Joseph of Gallia... What is he plotting?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.69,0:23:32.59,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:35.67,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use my powers for \Nsomething that horrid!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.67,0:23:37.96,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: \NThe Incompetent King Gone Mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.86,0:23:41.00,Next-Ep-Title,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(255,1)}The Incompetent King Gone Mad
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:41.00,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Saito, come save me quickly.
